10
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,400
You must save her.

11
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,000
Junior sister.

12
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:43,330
So she's Yan Jiehuan, the eldest daughter of Historian Yan.

13
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,120
Why are you just standing there?

14
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,039
Save her now!

15
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,640
When the poison from the arrow tree enters the bloodstream,

16
