How did Junior Sister get poisoned?

20
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,140
Who did this to her?

21
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,320
I am responsible.

22
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,320
Your Majesty.

23
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,000
Your Majesty.

24
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,840
I command you to use any means,

25
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,520
any remedy,

26
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,640
to save her life.

27
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,480
Only the Lone Tree herb can help.

28
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,320
However, this herb only grows around the arrow trees.

29
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:29,280
