30
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:32,000
those without medical knowledge can hardly identify it.

31
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,800
Then what should we do?

32
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,520
Taste it.

33
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,240
The herb has a sweet taste,

34
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,720
while regular grass tastes bitter.

35
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,760
Let me try.

36
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,560
I'm sorry,

37
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,610
I already have someone in my heart.

38
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,240
