53
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,800
Don't you realize if this gets exposed,

54
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,970
it will ruin everything I've planned.

55
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:11,360
If I become Empress,

56
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,240
wouldn't you benefit from it too, Uncle?

57
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,080
You're incompetent,

58
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,880
yet excellent at causing trouble.

59
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,140
The Empress isn't so easily eliminated.

60
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,080
If you dare act on your own again,

61
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:22,340
I'll flay both you and your mother alive.

62
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,720
Listen to me,

63
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:26,450
you must not let your guard down in the days ahead.

64
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,680
Lady Chunyu.

65
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,159
I found it.

66
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,840
How is that possible?

67
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,480
I tasted it. It was sweet.

68
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,420
This is just ordinary knotgrass,

69
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,240
slightly sweet, that's all.

70
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,440
That's right, this is it.

71
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,980
Junior Sister, you're awake.

72
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,920
I never thought you would care about her so much,

73
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,000
it really surprises me.

74
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:46,360
She saved my life,

75
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,000
I owe her a debt of gratitude.

76
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,200
Is it really just gratitude,

77
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,720
or is it love?

78
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:57,920
For ten years, do you know that you've always been

79
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:00,320
the one in my heart whom I both love and hate,

80
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,100
the one I can never forget.

81
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,580
Ten years ago, I brought you misfortune,

82
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,170
and now I drink your poison.

83
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,250
Whether it's hatred

84
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,000
or love,

85
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,920
everything has changed.

86
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,760
Your Majesty,

