and have recently captured both Wusha and Yata cities.

90
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,960
I request Your Majesty to dispatch troops immediately

91
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,820
to demonstrate the might of our Great Jing Kingdom.

92
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,520
Your Majesty, Minister Chen speaks the truth.

93
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:47,280
Such a tiny nation dares to be so arrogant.

94
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,480
We must fight

95
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,450
to show the power of our Great Jing.

96
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:54,360
Your Majesty, our enemies remain determined to invade Great Jing,

97
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,600
our military must be strengthened.

98
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,320
I believe the military budget should be increased.

99
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,280
Since I ascended the throne,

100
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:09,140
the military budget has been raised three times, and now you want another increase.

101
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:14,000
I know you still suspect me of killing our father,

102
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:16,000
but I assure you,

103
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:19,320
I had nothing to do with it.

104
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,760
Your Majesty.

105
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,400
On my way back from Shu Prefecture, I found something special

106
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,290
that I'd like to share with you.

107
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,760
Your Majesty, this item is extremely rare,

108
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,640
there's only a small amount.

109
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:40,240
Please, enjoy it carefully.

110
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,480
Oh no!

111
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,440
I'm sorry, Your Majesty.

112
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,280
I don't deserve such praise.

113
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,480
It truly is a pity.

114
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:10,520
By the way, Your Majesty, why did you summon me today?

115
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,680
Well,

116
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,600
when Father was alive,

117
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,800
