118
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:19,060
He secretly sent people to investigate,

119
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:22,200
but unfortunately, those sent were either killed

120
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,320
or bribed.

121
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,520
Now that you've returned,

122
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,040
I wish

123
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,680
to entrust this matter to you.

124
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,800
Aren't you afraid I'll refuse?

125
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,800
You won't,

126
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,480
because you also don't want to see the kingdom of Da Jing

127
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,840
ruined in our hands.

128
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:42,200
Your Majesty, although the ministers have a point,

129
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,200
North Yuan is merely a tiny state

130
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,460
not worth mentioning.

131
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,640
