136
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,600
military expenses keep increasing,

137
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,000
yet our forces continue to diminish.

138
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,400
This matter requires a thorough investigation.
